    Class ReusableCache

    This class act as a context for instantiated items. It efficiently keeps track of the instantiated items and pools them when they finish their purpose. When you destroy this class it removes all the pools that are created for items. See PushCache(ReusableCache) and ControlledPopCache(ReusableCache).
